name: CSS
format:
<style>
    .nr-dashboard-theme {
        min-width: 1080px;
        max-width: 1080px;
        padding: 0px auto;
        margin: 0px auto;
        background-color: black !important;
    }
    .nr-dashboard-cardcontainer {
        /* groups background */
        background-color: black !important;
    }
    .led .nr-dashboard-template {
        /* led background */
        background-color: black !important;
    }
    .level {
        /* level background */
        background-color: black !important;
    }
    .level .nr-dashboard-template {
        /* level background */
        background-color: black !important;
        border-style: solid;
        border-width: 1px;
        border-color: #636669;
     }


    .guage {
        background-color: #263238 !important;
    }
    .guage .nr-dashboard-gauge-title {
        /* guage title font */
        color: #d7ded9 !important;
    }
    .guage .nr-dashboard-gauge text {
        /* guage value text color */
        fill: white !important;
    }


    .guage2 {
        background-color: black !important;
    }
    .guage2 .nr-dashboard-gauge-title {
        /* guage title font */
        color: white !important;
    }
    .guage2 .nr-dashboard-gauge text {
        /* guage value text color */
        fill: white !important;
    }


    .highlighted {
        /* highlight important values */
        background-color: #aacfe3 !important;
        color: black !important;
        }
    .highlighted .nr-dashboard-gauge text {
        /* text color */
        fill: black !important;
    }

    .nr-dashboard-ui_led {
    }
    .nr-dashboard-ui_level {
    }
    .nr-dashboard-theme .label {
    }

    
    .borders {
        border-style: solid;
        border-width: 1px;
        border-color: #636669;
    }
    .font10 {
        font-size: 10px;
    }
    .font14 {
         font-size: 16px;
    }
    .labels {
        /* label background */
        background-color: #101826 !important;
    }
    .labels .label {
        /* sets labels font color,
        needs .label to apply */
        color: #5d7eba !important;
    }
    .labels .value {
        /* ui text value color */
        color: white  !important;
    }
    .labels-2 {
    /* label background */
    background-color: #101826 !important;
    }
    .labels-2 .label {
        /* sets labels font color */
        color: #818999 !important;    }
    .labels-2 .value {
        /* sets labels font color */
        color: #818999 !important;
    }
    .titles12 {
        /* yellow titles */
        font-size: 12px;
        color: yellow !important;
    }
    [class*='led_'] {
        /* led borders */
        border-style: solid;
        border-width: 0px;
        border-color: #6e6363;
